{
  "stem": "1496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They brought them to the Polish border, and they loaded them out by the border.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Polish government didn't want to let them in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The German government didn't want to let them back, and they stayed for a while over there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then after a while, the Polish government decided to let the people in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were brought into-- and even some of relatives of ours, which were also in this situation, came to stay with us because they didn't have any housing for a while.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So this you felt before the war already-- influence of Nazi Germany, and even in Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, our life changed immediately, because, as you know, right after the Nazi occupied Poland and Krakow, Jews had to be identified on the street by wearing the armband with the Jewish star on it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were exposed to harassment, to all kinds of forced labor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And however, in the 1940s, already, our father experienced the main problem, because one of the Nazis similar to Schindler came to Poland and presented-- one day, presented my father with a document, and took over our business.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And became so-called troyhandler, which is, actually, got in charge.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father had to work in the business, and-- because he didn't know how to handle it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But actually, all the proceeds and everything was taken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He took over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't get paid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody got paid, but we had to still be-- and they wouldn't give us any pay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- by the way, I was already in the business, because since I graduated high school, I joined my father's business and started working in it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, when the Nazi took over, the business shortly afterwards, I really left, because I saw there was no room for me over there.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
